# 💬 NEURA CHAT - AI-Powered Chat Application

![NEURA CHAT Demo](frontend/src/assets/logo.png)

A modern, AI-powered chat application with file upload support, conversation history, and user authentication.

## ✨ Features

- 🤖 **AI Chat** - Intelligent conversations using Groq AI (LLaMA 3.1)
- 📱 **Responsive** - Works on desktop & mobile
- 🔐 **Authentication** - Secure JWT-based auth
- 💾 **Chat History** - Save and manage conversations
- 📎 **File Upload** - Support for PDF, DOCX, TXT
- 📝 **Markdown** - Formatted AI responses
- 🔄 **Regenerate** - Reroll AI responses
- ⭐ **Feedback** - Rate responses with thumbs up/down

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Frontend:** React, Vite, TailwindCSS, Axios
**Backend:** Python, FastAPI, SQLAlchemy, MySQL, JWT
**AI:** Groq API (LLaMA 3.1)

## 🚀 Live Demo

- **Frontend:** [https://neura-aii.netlify.app/](https://neura-aii.netlify.app/)
- **Backend API:** [https://neura-ai-vvfv.onrender.com](https://neura-ai-vvfv.onrender.com)


